      <event start="T1186-593" end="T1189-393">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1189-393" end="T1190-604">Ne, ampak </event>
      <event start="T1190-604" end="T1192-371">te stvari so mene pushale through. </event>
      <event start="T1192-371" end="T1193-755">Osnovna šola. </event>
      <event start="T1193-755" end="T374">Jaz bi(), </event>
      <event start="T374" end="T375">če jaz če ne bi imela Harryja Potterja, jaz ne bi naredila osnovne šole, </event>
      <event start="T375" end="T1197-425">meni je prav žal. </event>
      <event start="T1199-316" end="T1200-051">Emo. </event>
      <event start="T1200-637" end="T1203-02">[zvok] Ooo. </event>
      <event start="T1203-02" end="T1204-438">Emo. </event>
      <event start="T1204-438" end="T376">K vedno sem tako: </event>
      <event start="T376" end="T377">"Dobro, </event>
      <event start="T377" end="T378">pa saj nisem nisem bila tako emo, k sem bila majhna, </event>
      <event start="T378" end="T379">right?" </event>
      <event start="T379" end="T380">In pol grem gledat tako stare slike </event>
      <event start="T380" end="T381">in sem tako: </event>
      <event start="T381" end="T1211-11">"O, moj bog." </event>
      <event start="T1212-826" end="T383">No, it's not. </event>
      <event start="T383" end="T1214-719">It's really not. [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T1218-778" end="T1221-47">You can take emo out of me? [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T1221-47" end="T1222-101">Ne. </event>
      <event start="T1222-101" end="T384">You can take </event>
      <event start="T384" end="T385">you can take me away from emo </event>
      <event start="T385" end="T1229-435">and you can take [jezik] emo out of me. [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T1229-925" end="T1231-536">To si+bom tetovirala ... </event>
      <event start="T1232-189" end="T1233-34">čez prsi. </event>
      <event start="T1233-34" end="T1236-926">[smeh] </event>
    </tier>
    <tier id="COLLOQ_ROG-dialog-0033" speaker="ROG-dialog-0033" category="colloq" type="a" display-name="ROG-dialog-0033 [colloq]">
      <event start="T2-027" end="T2">A veš, </event>
      <event start="T2" end="T3-601">ko me boli zob pač. </event>
      <event start="T4-87" end="T6-711">Tko ... </event>
      <event start="T6-711" end="T10-484">Že k@kšna dv() dva tedna nazaj sem šla prvič k zobozdravnici. </event>
      <event start="T10-918" end="T12-724">In ... </event>
      <event start="T12-724" end="T4">je ona men eee lepu ... nardila novo plombo, </event>
      <event start="T4" end="T17-967">ker mi je ta stara odstopla. </event>
      <event start="T18-611" end="T19-378">Eem ... </event>
      <event start="T19-378" end="T20-829">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T20-829" end="T5">in tm še neki popravla </event>
      <event start="T5" end="T6">pa neki mi je namazala kle pr dlesni kao, </event>
      <event start="T6" end="T25-932">k me je skelel pa to. </event>
      <event start="T26-552" end="T28-937">Eem ... in ... </event>
      <event start="T28-937" end="T30-41">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T30-41" end="T32-342">nasled@n teden sem mogla spet prid@t. </event>
      <event start="T32-342" end="T33-825">In mene še kr ... </event>
      <event start="T33-825" end="T35-594">Pač k je mogla še neki na nov narest </event>
      <event start="T35-594" end="T39-472">pa vmes sem se šla še slikat eee zobne krone. </event>
      <event start="T39-472" end="T10">In eem pridem nazaj </event>
      <event start="T10" end="T11">in mene še kr ta zob s plombo najbol boli, </event>
      <event start="T11" end="T44-318">a ne? </event>
      <event start="T44-578" end="T12">In jaz njej povem: </event>
      <event start="T12" end="T13">"Ta zob me še kr boli, </event>
      <event start="T13" end="T47-9">najb@l." </event>
      <event start="T48-787" end="T14">Ona tko: </event>
      <event start="T14" end="T15">"Ja, jaz v bistvu nč ne vidim, da bi blo kej narobe," </event>
      <event start="T15" end="T52-243">a ne. </event>
      <event start="T52-243" end="T16">In jz tko: </event>
      <event start="T16" end="T54-558">"Mhm, super, super." </event>
      <event start="T55-989" end="T57-615">In eem ... </event>
      <event start="T57-615" end="T17">ona mi vse poprav, </event>
      <event start="T17" end="T59-232">bla bla bla. </event>
      <event start="T59-232" end="T18">Mine en teden, </event>
      <event start="T18" end="T62-429">mene začne to svinsko bolet, </event>
      <event start="T62-429" end="T64-13">pač tko, svinsko. </event>
      <event start="T64-683" end="T19">Tko da, ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T19" end="T66-663">pet minut me najb@l boli, </event>
      <event start="T66-663" end="T68-523">tko utripa. </event>
      <event start="T68-523" end="T69-175">Ja ja. </event>
      <event start="T70-555" end="T20">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T20" end="T73-684">pač to me je zej tko ta teden začel tko bolet. </event>
      <event start="T73-684" end="T75-573">Tko u pondelk, tork. </event>
      <event start="T75-573" end="T76-794">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T76-794" end="T22">In poj men to začne bolet, </event>
      <event start="T22" end="T80-363">tko da mi prov utripa, tko ... </event>
      <event start="T80-363" end="T23">pet minut mi utripa, </event>
      <event start="T23" end="T83-991">tko boli me, ko da mi en vrta v zob pač, </event>
      <event start="T83-991" end="T86-91">pa sploh ne morem določ@t, kje je ta bolečina. </event>
      <event start="T87-482" end="T89-152">Eem ... </event>
      <event start="T89-152" end="T24">in jz tko, </event>
      <event start="T24" end="T91-518">to se zej dogaja ene štir dni. </event>
      <event start="T92-19" end="T94-766">Kličem zobarco v četrtek dopoldne. </event>
      <event start="T94-766" end="T96-169">[zvok] "A loh prosim pridem?" </event>
      <event start="T96-169" end="T97-651">Pač nočem, nočem težit </event>
      <event start="T97-651" end="T99-321">pa že kle v ta treto eee ... </event>
      <event start="T99-321" end="T25">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T25" end="T26">plis, </event>
      <event start="T26" end="T101-031">a lahko pridem. </event>
      <event start="T101-031" end="T102-028">In je bla tko: </event>
      <event start="T102-028" end="T27">"Ja dons je sam do enih, </event>
      <event start="T27" end="T104-873">a lahko prideš zdele takoj?" </event>
      <event start="T104-873" end="T28">In itak nisem mela avta </event>
      <event start="T28" end="T107-922">in nisem mogla prid@t takoj. </event>
      <event start="T107-922" end="T110-148">In mi je rekla, da moram na dežurno. </event>
      <event start="T110-796" end="T29">In pol sem se jz odločla, </event>
      <event start="T29" end="T30">okej, </event>
      <event start="T30" end="T113-89">jutr dopoldne grem na dežurno. </event>
      <event start="T113-89" end="T31">Kličem jz v petek, </event>
      <event start="T31" end="T116-022">šest trideset. </event>
      <event start="T116-701" end="T32">Na dežurno, </event>
      <event start="T32" end="T119-848">v Bistrco h uni, ta grozni. </event>
      <event start="T121-399" end="T121-743">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T122-33" end="T122-954">Senji. </event>
      <event start="T123-733" end="T124-326">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T124-326" end="T125-355">Kličem. </event>
      <event start="T125-355" end="T126-379">Nuben se ne oglasi. </event>
      <event start="T126-379" end="T34">Zaprto. </event>
      <event start="T34" end="T129-006">Ja, "s() ... </event>
      <event start="T129-006" end="T35">sledite seznamu na zdravst() na spletni strani zdravstvenega doma". </event>
      <event start="T35" end="T132-816">Jz ... </event>
      <event start="T132-816" end="T36">v redu, </event>
      <event start="T36" end="T134-651">pogledam. </event>
      <event start="T134-651" end="T37">Tam piše pač, da nek tip, </event>
      <event start="T37" end="T136-419">a ne. </event>
      <event start="T137-711" end="T38">Jz kličem njega, </event>
      <event start="T38" end="T139-646">ob sedmih. </event>
      <event start="T139-646" end="T141-27">Pisal je, da ob sedmih on začne delat. </event>
      <event start="T141-574" end="T39">Kličem ga pet čez sedem, </event>
      <event start="T39" end="T144-181">noben se ne jav. </event>
      <event start="T147-598" end="T40">Ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T40" end="T148-747">nimam pojma. </event>
      <event start="T149-748" end="T42">Pač po moje, da ... s() je stalno tm, </event>
      <event start="T42" end="T43">ampak pol ma tko svoje paciente </event>
      <event start="T43" end="T155-191">pa poj še dežura kdaj. </event>
      <event start="T156-201" end="T45">No, </event>
      <event start="T45" end="T46">kličem, </event>
      <event start="T46" end="T160-119">se oglasi tajnica: </event>
      <event start="T160-119" end="T47">"Ja, </event>
      <event start="T47" end="T48">eee, </event>
      <event start="T48" end="T49">odpiralni čas te ordinacije, </event>
      <event start="T49" end="T50">eee, </event>
      <event start="T50" end="T165-739">pač klicali ste izven tega časa." </event>
      <event start="T166-397" end="T168-172">In pol pove čas. </event>
      <event start="T168-172" end="T169-851">Šest trideset do trinajst. </event>
      <event start="T169-851" end="T172-294">Ura ... sedem nič pet. </event>
      <event start="T172-975" end="T51">Kličem na front ofis, </event>
      <event start="T51" end="T176-099">pač tm front desk. </event>
      <event start="T176-837" end="T177-851">Zdravstveni dom. </event>
      <event start="T177-851" end="T179-388">Zakaj se men nuben ne jav? </event>
      <event start="T179-388" end="T52">Pač kdo ma dons dežurstvo, </event>
      <event start="T52" end="T181-035">a ne? </event>
      <event start="T181-465" end="T53">In tko: </event>
      <event start="T53" end="T54">"Ja, </event>
      <event start="T54" end="T55">sej ma on, </event>
      <event start="T55" end="T184-731">sej, sej bo pršu." [zvok] </event>
      <event start="T184-731" end="T186-012">Vat du ju min, [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T186-012" end="T188-490">tko petinšt@rdeset minut že zamuja na šiht. </event>
      <event start="T194-119" end="T194-571">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T194-571" end="T195-585">Aj tink so. </event>
      <event start="T195-585" end="T196-546">Misl@m, </event>
      <event start="T196-546" end="T57">tko se je tud men zdel, </event>
      <event start="T57" end="T199-602">ampak aj ges not. </event>
      <event start="T199-602" end="T60">Kličem čez petnajst minut spet, </event>
      <event start="T60" end="T203-189">se mi oglasi ta njegova sestra. </event>
      <event start="T203-189" end="T204-418">Najb@l tko: </event>
      <event start="T204-418" end="T205-539">"Mi mamo najb@l, največ dela, največ pacientov že tko naročenih, </event>
      <event start="T205-539" end="T207-395">k so eee tuki pač pra() prov pacienti, </event>
      <event start="T207-395" end="T212-768">in pol še te, k jih vse neki boli." </event>
      <event start="T212-768" end="T213-717">In jz tko: </event>
      <event start="T213-717" end="T62">"Okej, </event>
      <event start="T62" end="T216-135">mene tud boli pač. </event>
      <event start="T216-135" end="T217-133">Plis, plis." </event>
      <event start="T217-874" end="T63">Una tko: </event>
      <event start="T63" end="T64">"Ja, </event>
      <event start="T64" end="T65">petnejst do desetih pridte." </event>
      <event start="T65" end="T66">In jz tko: </event>
      <event start="T66" end="T220-91">"Oki." </event>
      <event start="T220-91" end="T222-598">"Pa zih boste mogl kej počakat." </event>
      <event start="T222-598" end="T223-453">"V redu." </event>
      <event start="T224-943" end="T225-445">Ja, ja. </event>
      <event start="T226-456" end="T227-157">V redu. </event>
      <event start="T227-157" end="T228-28">Pridem tja ... </event>
      <event start="T228-28" end="T229-744">Nobenga v čakalnici, </event>
      <event start="T229-744" end="T67">sama sedim, </event>
      <event start="T67" end="T231-239">sama sedim. </event>
      <event start="T231-239" end="T232-571">Čez pet minut ... </event>
      <event start="T232-571" end="T234-096">to se prav ene deset do, </event>
      <event start="T234-096" end="T68">on odpre vrata, </event>
      <event start="T68" end="T236-004">noben ne pride ven, </event>
      <event start="T236-004" end="T236-858">nobenga ni blo noter. </event>
      <event start="T238-04" end="T69">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T69" end="T238-718">nobenga ni b(), </event>
      <event start="T238-718" end="T70">jz tko, </event>
      <event start="T70" end="T239-937">on tko: </event>
      <event start="T239-937" end="T71">"Sara?" </event>
      <event start="T71" end="T72">In jz tko: </event>
      <event start="T72" end="T241-333">"Ja." </event>
      <event start="T241-333" end="T242-658">Grem noter. </event>
      <event start="T242-658" end="T245-306">Ta dohtar se najb@l prtužuje. </event>
      <event start="T245-627" end="T73">Najb@l! </event>
      <event start="T73" end="T247-172">[smeh] Tko prov ... </event>
      <event start="T247-172" end="T74">"Ja tko ... </event>
      <event start="T74" end="T75">k da sem jz tuki za vse, </event>
      <event start="T75" end="T76">bom jz vse zrihtu, </event>
      <event start="T76" end="T251-425">vaa neki." </event>
      <event start="T251-81" end="T252-61">Ne men osebno, </event>
      <event start="T252-61" end="T253-806">ampak tko že prej. </event>
      <event start="T253-806" end="T255-577">In pol še ena gospa kliče </event>
      <event start="T255-577" end="T78">in je bla tko: </event>
      <event start="T78" end="T79">"Ja, </event>
      <event start="T79" end="T259-040">ta plomba neki neki ni v redu." </event>
      <event start="T259-040" end="T259-687">Pač tko ... neki se je prtožvala, </event>
      <event start="T259-687" end="T262-41">pa da rab mmm neki na nov. </event>
      <event start="T264-081" end="T264-524">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T264-524" end="T82">In on tko: </event>
      <event start="T82" end="T267-072">"Če b jz mel tako ženo, </event>
      <event start="T268-106" end="T83">pet let zdržiš, </event>
      <event start="T83" end="T269-924">pol te pa pobere." </event>
      <event start="T269-924" end="T270-891">In jz tko. </event>
      <event start="T272-076" end="T272-943">V@T@F@ pač. </event>
      <event start="T274-68" end="T276-294">Onedva sta se najb@l tko ... </event>
      <event start="T276-294" end="T277-655">najb@l sta ... </event>
      <event start="T277-655" end="T277-971">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T281-373" end="T281-959">No ... </event>
      <event start="T282-742" end="T283-787">In on tko men: </event>
      <event start="T283-787" end="T285-039">"A dam enekcijo?" </event>
      <event start="T285-039" end="T286-086">In jz tko: </event>
