      <event start="T346" end="T1095-438">ko j že njej ime? </event>
      <event start="T1096-274" end="T347">Bela, </event>
      <event start="T347" end="T1098-214">pač, jz bi hotla bit ona. </event>
      <event start="T1099-852" end="T1101-610">Pa tko tm žvet v temu mestecu. </event>
      <event start="T1101-610" end="T1102-178">Odfuk. </event>
      <event start="T1111-569" end="T353">No, </event>
      <event start="T353" end="T1112-904">do tja pa nisem pršla. </event>
      <event start="T1114-371" end="T1115-889">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1118-739" end="T1119-192">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1122-862" end="T1123-466">Pa zih ni. </event>
      <event start="T1126-614" end="T1127-688">O, ne. </event>
      <event start="T1127-688" end="T1128-311">O, ne. </event>
      <event start="T1134-524" end="T1134-786">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1141-845" end="T1143-647">Ko se že temu reče? </event>
      <event start="T1145-138" end="T1145-692">Ja ja. </event>
      <event start="T1146-369" end="T1147-643">_@nkeni veli. </event>
      <event start="T1151-172" end="T366">Ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T366" end="T367">men se zdi, da če bi gledala </event>
      <event start="T367" end="T1155-648">eem ... </event>
      <event start="T1155-648" end="T368">Kva sem zd(), </event>
      <event start="T368" end="T369">ka sem zdej gledala, k sem bla tud tko, </event>
      <event start="T369" end="T1161-328">če b jz to gledala, k bi bla tko mlajša ... </event>
      <event start="T1161-328" end="T1163-134">Ne bi blo dobr. </event>
      <event start="T1163-134" end="T1163-941">Tko Hanger, </event>
      <event start="T1163-941" end="T370">ja, </event>
      <event start="T370" end="T1165-271">Hanger Gejms. </event>
      <event start="T1165-271" end="T1167-023">Zanč sem gledala Hanger Gejms. </event>
      <event start="T1167-023" end="T1168-510">Ko se temu reče? </event>
      <event start="T1169-537" end="T1170-253">Igre lakote. </event>
      <event start="T1172-121" end="T1173-634">Še dobr, da tega nisem prej gledala. </event>
      <event start="T1175-826" end="T1176-411">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1176-411" end="T371">Sam je bla tko ... </event>
      <event start="T371" end="T1178-978">dis is so dip. [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T1179-655" end="T1179-938">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1181-396" end="T373">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T373" end="T1183-126">To bi bla jz pač. </event>
      <event start="T1183-937" end="T1186-593">Po moje, da bi bla že bl redikalajzd kokr zdej. </event>
      <event start="T1186-593" end="T1189-393">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1189-393" end="T1190-604">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1197-425" end="T1200-637">Jz, če ne bi mela mojih imo ... skupin. </event>
      <event start="T1211-11" end="T382">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T382" end="T1212-826">is its not dž@st hav ju luk. [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T1216-266" end="T1218-778">[smeh] To, kar je v tebi, je pomembno. </event>
      <event start="T1227-262" end="T1228-13">To pa ne vem. </event>
      <event start="T1229-435" end="T1229-925">Tru. </event>
      <event start="T1231-536" end="T1232-189">To je resnica. </event>
      <event start="T1233-34" end="T1236-926">[smeh] </event>
    </tier>
    <tier id="TIE2_NORM1" speaker="ROG-dialog-0033" category="norm" type="t" display-name="ROG-dialog-0033 [norm]">
      <event start="T2-027" end="T2">A veš, </event>
      <event start="T2" end="T3-601">kako me boli zob pač. </event>
      <event start="T4-87" end="T6-711">Tako ... </event>
      <event start="T6-711" end="T10-484">Že kakšna dv() dva tedna nazaj sem šla prvič k zobozdravnici. </event>
      <event start="T10-918" end="T12-724">In ... </event>
      <event start="T12-724" end="T4">je ona meni eee lepo ... naredila novo plombo, </event>
      <event start="T4" end="T17-967">ker mi je ta stara odstopila. </event>
      <event start="T18-611" end="T19-378">Eem ... </event>
      <event start="T19-378" end="T20-829">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T20-829" end="T5">in tam še nekaj popravila </event>
      <event start="T5" end="T6">pa nekaj mi je namazala tule pri dlesni kao, </event>
      <event start="T6" end="T25-932">k me je skelelo pa to. </event>
      <event start="T26-552" end="T28-937">Eem ... in ... </event>
      <event start="T28-937" end="T30-41">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T30-41" end="T32-342">naslednji teden sem mogla spet priti. </event>
      <event start="T32-342" end="T33-825">In mene še kar ... </event>
      <event start="T33-825" end="T35-594">Pač k je mogla še nekaj na novo narediti </event>
      <event start="T35-594" end="T39-472">pa vmes sem se šla še slikat eee zobne krone. </event>
      <event start="T39-472" end="T10">In eem pridem nazaj </event>
      <event start="T10" end="T11">in mene še kar ta zob s plombo najbolj boli, </event>
      <event start="T11" end="T44-318">a ne? </event>
      <event start="T44-578" end="T12">In jaz njej povem: </event>
      <event start="T12" end="T13">"Ta zob me še kar boli, </event>
      <event start="T13" end="T47-9">najbolj." </event>
      <event start="T48-787" end="T14">Ona tako: </event>
      <event start="T14" end="T15">"Ja, jaz v bistvu nič ne vidim, da bi bilo kaj narobe," </event>
      <event start="T15" end="T52-243">a ne. </event>
      <event start="T52-243" end="T16">In jaz tako: </event>
      <event start="T16" end="T54-558">"Mhm, super, super." </event>
      <event start="T55-989" end="T57-615">In eem ... </event>
      <event start="T57-615" end="T17">ona mi vse popravi, </event>
      <event start="T17" end="T59-232">bla bla bla. </event>
      <event start="T59-232" end="T18">Mine en teden, </event>
      <event start="T18" end="T62-429">mene začne to svinjsko boleti, </event>
      <event start="T62-429" end="T64-13">pač tako, svinjsko. </event>
      <event start="T64-683" end="T19">Tako da, ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T19" end="T66-663">pet minut me najbolj boli, </event>
      <event start="T66-663" end="T68-523">tako utripa. </event>
      <event start="T68-523" end="T69-175">Ja ja. </event>
      <event start="T70-555" end="T20">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T20" end="T73-684">pač to me je zdaj tako ta teden začelo tako boleti. </event>
      <event start="T73-684" end="T75-573">Tako v ponedeljek, torek. </event>
      <event start="T75-573" end="T76-794">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T76-794" end="T22">In pol mene to začne boleti, </event>
      <event start="T22" end="T80-363">tako da mi prav utripa, tako ... </event>
      <event start="T80-363" end="T23">pet minut mi utripa, </event>
      <event start="T23" end="T83-991">tako boli me, kot da mi en vrta v zob pač, </event>
      <event start="T83-991" end="T86-91">pa sploh ne morem določiti, kje je ta bolečina. </event>
      <event start="T87-482" end="T89-152">Eem ... </event>
      <event start="T89-152" end="T24">in jaz tako, </event>
      <event start="T24" end="T91-518">to se zdaj dogaja ene štiri dni. </event>
      <event start="T92-19" end="T94-766">Kličem zobarico v četrtek dopoldne. </event>
      <event start="T94-766" end="T96-169">[zvok] "A lahko prosim pridem?" </event>
      <event start="T96-169" end="T97-651">Pač nočem, nočem težiti </event>
      <event start="T97-651" end="T99-321">pa že tule v ta tretje eee ... </event>
      <event start="T99-321" end="T25">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T25" end="T26">please, </event>
      <event start="T26" end="T101-031">a lahko pridem. </event>
      <event start="T101-031" end="T102-028">In je bila tako: </event>
      <event start="T102-028" end="T27">"Ja danes je samo do enih, </event>
      <event start="T27" end="T104-873">a lahko prideš zdajle takoj?" </event>
      <event start="T104-873" end="T28">In itak nisem imela avta </event>
      <event start="T28" end="T107-922">in nisem mogla priti takoj. </event>
      <event start="T107-922" end="T110-148">In mi je rekla, da moram na dežurno. </event>
      <event start="T110-796" end="T29">In pol sem se jaz odločila, </event>
      <event start="T29" end="T30">okej, </event>
      <event start="T30" end="T113-89">jutri dopoldne grem na dežurno. </event>
      <event start="T113-89" end="T31">Kličem jaz v petek, </event>
      <event start="T31" end="T116-022">šest trideset. </event>
      <event start="T116-701" end="T32">Na dežurno, </event>
      <event start="T32" end="T119-848">v Bistrico k oni, ta grozni. </event>
      <event start="T121-399" end="T121-743">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T122-33" end="T122-954">Senji. </event>
      <event start="T123-733" end="T124-326">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T124-326" end="T125-355">Kličem. </event>
      <event start="T125-355" end="T126-379">Noben se ne oglasi. </event>
      <event start="T126-379" end="T34">Zaprto. </event>
      <event start="T34" end="T129-006">Ja, "s() ... </event>
      <event start="T129-006" end="T35">sledite seznamu na zdravst() na spletni strani zdravstvenega doma". </event>
      <event start="T35" end="T132-816">Jaz ... </event>
      <event start="T132-816" end="T36">v redu, </event>
      <event start="T36" end="T134-651">pogledam. </event>
      <event start="T134-651" end="T37">Tam piše pač, da neki tip, </event>
      <event start="T37" end="T136-419">a ne. </event>
      <event start="T137-711" end="T38">Jaz kličem njega, </event>
      <event start="T38" end="T139-646">ob sedmih. </event>
      <event start="T139-646" end="T141-27">Pisalo je, da ob sedmih on začne delati. </event>
      <event start="T141-574" end="T39">Kličem ga pet čez sedem, </event>
      <event start="T39" end="T144-181">noben se ne javi. </event>
      <event start="T147-598" end="T40">Ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T40" end="T148-747">nimam pojma. </event>
      <event start="T149-748" end="T42">Pač po moje, da ... s() je stalno tam, </event>
      <event start="T42" end="T43">ampak pol ima tako svoje paciente </event>
      <event start="T43" end="T155-191">pa pol še dežura kdaj. </event>
      <event start="T156-201" end="T45">No, </event>
      <event start="T45" end="T46">kličem, </event>
      <event start="T46" end="T160-119">se oglasi tajnica: </event>
      <event start="T160-119" end="T47">"Ja, </event>
      <event start="T47" end="T48">eee, </event>
      <event start="T48" end="T49">odpiralni čas te ordinacije, </event>
      <event start="T49" end="T50">eee, </event>
      <event start="T50" end="T165-739">pač klicali ste izven tega časa." </event>
      <event start="T166-397" end="T168-172">In pol pove čas. </event>
      <event start="T168-172" end="T169-851">Šest trideset do trinajst. </event>
      <event start="T169-851" end="T172-294">Ura ... sedem nič pet. </event>
      <event start="T172-975" end="T51">Kličem na front office, </event>
      <event start="T51" end="T176-099">pač tam front desk. </event>
      <event start="T176-837" end="T177-851">Zdravstveni dom. </event>
      <event start="T177-851" end="T179-388">Zakaj se meni noben ne javi? </event>
      <event start="T179-388" end="T52">Pač kdo ima danes dežurstvo, </event>
      <event start="T52" end="T181-035">a ne? </event>
      <event start="T181-465" end="T53">In tako: </event>
      <event start="T53" end="T54">"Ja, </event>
      <event start="T54" end="T55">saj ima on, </event>
      <event start="T55" end="T184-731">saj, saj bo prišel." [zvok] </event>
      <event start="T184-731" end="T186-012">What do you mean, [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T186-012" end="T188-490">tako petinštirideset minut že zamuja na šiht. </event>
      <event start="T194-119" end="T194-571">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T194-571" end="T195-585">I think so. </event>
      <event start="T195-585" end="T196-546">Mislim, </event>
      <event start="T196-546" end="T57">tako se je tudi meni zdelo, </event>
      <event start="T57" end="T199-602">ampak I guess not. </event>
      <event start="T199-602" end="T60">Kličem čez petnajst minut spet, </event>
      <event start="T60" end="T203-189">se mi oglasi ta njegova sestra. </event>
      <event start="T203-189" end="T204-418">Najbolj tako: </event>
      <event start="T204-418" end="T205-539">"Mi imamo najbolj, največ dela, največ pacientov že tako naročenih, </event>
      <event start="T205-539" end="T207-395">k so eee tukaj pač pra() prav pacienti, </event>
      <event start="T207-395" end="T212-768">in pol še te, k jih vse nekaj boli." </event>
      <event start="T212-768" end="T213-717">In jaz tako: </event>
      <event start="T213-717" end="T62">"Okej, </event>
      <event start="T62" end="T216-135">mene tudi boli pač. </event>
      <event start="T216-135" end="T217-133">Please, please." </event>
      <event start="T217-874" end="T63">Ona tako: </event>
      <event start="T63" end="T64">"Ja, </event>
      <event start="T64" end="T65">petnajst do desetih pridite." </event>
      <event start="T65" end="T66">In jaz tako: </event>
      <event start="T66" end="T220-91">"Okej." </event>
      <event start="T220-91" end="T222-598">"Pa ziher boste mogli kaj počakati." </event>
      <event start="T222-598" end="T223-453">"V redu." </event>
      <event start="T224-943" end="T225-445">Ja, ja. </event>
      <event start="T226-456" end="T227-157">V redu. </event>
      <event start="T227-157" end="T228-28">Pridem tja ... </event>
      <event start="T228-28" end="T229-744">Nobenega v čakalnici, </event>
      <event start="T229-744" end="T67">sama sedim, </event>
      <event start="T67" end="T231-239">sama sedim. </event>
      <event start="T231-239" end="T232-571">Čez pet minut ... </event>
      <event start="T232-571" end="T234-096">to se pravi ene deset do, </event>
      <event start="T234-096" end="T68">on odpre vrata, </event>
      <event start="T68" end="T236-004">noben ne pride ven, </event>
      <event start="T236-004" end="T236-858">nobenega ni bilo noter. </event>
      <event start="T238-04" end="T69">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T69" end="T238-718">nobenega ni b(), </event>
      <event start="T238-718" end="T70">jaz tako, </event>
      <event start="T70" end="T239-937">on tako: </event>
      <event start="T239-937" end="T71">"Sara?" </event>
      <event start="T71" end="T72">In jaz tako: </event>
      <event start="T72" end="T241-333">"Ja." </event>
      <event start="T241-333" end="T242-658">Grem noter. </event>
      <event start="T242-658" end="T245-306">Ta dohtar se najbolj pritožuje. </event>
      <event start="T245-627" end="T73">Najbolj! </event>
      <event start="T73" end="T247-172">[smeh] Tako prav ... </event>
      <event start="T247-172" end="T74">"Ja tako ... </event>
      <event start="T74" end="T75">k da sem jaz tukaj za vse, </event>
      <event start="T75" end="T76">bom jaz vse zrihtal, </event>
      <event start="T76" end="T251-425">vaa nekaj." </event>
      <event start="T251-81" end="T252-61">Ne meni osebno, </event>
      <event start="T252-61" end="T253-806">ampak tako že prej. </event>
      <event start="T253-806" end="T255-577">In pol še ena gospa kliče </event>
      <event start="T255-577" end="T78">in je bila tako: </event>
      <event start="T78" end="T79">"Ja, </event>
      <event start="T79" end="T259-040">ta plomba nekaj nekaj ni v redu." </event>
      <event start="T259-040" end="T259-687">Pač tako ... nekaj se je pritoževala, </event>
      <event start="T259-687" end="T262-41">pa da rabi mmm nekaj na novo. </event>
      <event start="T264-081" end="T264-524">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T264-524" end="T82">In on tako: </event>
      <event start="T82" end="T267-072">"Če bi jaz imel tako ženo, </event>
      <event start="T268-106" end="T83">pet let zdržiš, </event>
      <event start="T83" end="T269-924">pol te pa pobere." </event>
      <event start="T269-924" end="T270-891">In jaz tako. </event>
      <event start="T272-076" end="T272-943">WTF pač. </event>
      <event start="T274-68" end="T276-294">Onadva sta se najbolj tako ... </event>
      <event start="T276-294" end="T277-655">najbolj sta ... </event>
      <event start="T277-655" end="T277-971">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T281-373" end="T281-959">No ... </event>
      <event start="T282-742" end="T283-787">In on tako meni: </event>
      <event start="T283-787" end="T285-039">"A dam injekcijo?" </event>
      <event start="T285-039" end="T286-086">In jaz tako: </event>
      <event start="T286-086" end="T289-244">"A ni to tvoj job, da veš, a mi daš injekcijo ali ne?" </event>
      <event start="T289-244" end="T290-091">In pol mi tako: </event>
      <event start="T290-091" end="T85">"Ja a hočete injekcijo, </event>
      <event start="T85" end="T292-105">pač da ne boste čutili?" </event>
      <event start="T292-105" end="T86">In jaz tako: </event>
      <event start="T86" end="T87">"Če mi boste odpirali zob, </event>
      <event start="T87" end="T296-08">prosim, dajte mi injekcijo pač." </event>
      <event start="T298-01" end="T88">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T88" end="T299-473">pač ono zato k k imam zavarovalnico, </event>
      <event start="T299-473" end="T300-974">a ne. </event>
      <event start="T300-974" end="T303-085">To še je šlo vse [nerazumljivo]. </event>
      <event start="T303-085" end="T91">Ampak on je meni dal tako račun, </event>
      <event start="T91" end="T92">mislim </event>
      <event start="T92" end="T305-162">ona je tam tako: </event>
      <event start="T305-162" end="T305-915">"Še račun počakajte." </event>
      <event start="T305-915" end="T306-571">In jaz tako: </event>
      <event start="T306-571" end="T93">"Kakšen račun?" </event>
      <event start="T93" end="T94">Pač, a veš, </event>
      <event start="T94" end="T309-311">tako sploh ... </event>
      <event start="T309-311" end="T311-963">Jaz sem samo zdravstveno kartico sabo pa nič drugega, </event>
      <event start="T311-963" end="T313-884">k sem ostalo vse v avtu pustila. </event>
      <event start="T313-884" end="T97">No ja, </event>
      <event start="T97" end="T315-44">in guess what? </event>
      <event start="T316-116" end="T98">Še kar me boli zob. </event>
      <event start="T98" end="T317-435">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T317-435" end="T99">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T99" end="T319-119">Zdaj je še slabše. </event>
      <event start="T319-119" end="T321-199">Ker zdaj me tudi na dotik boli. </event>
      <event start="T322-52" end="T322-981">Ne. </event>
      <event start="T323-534" end="T325-118">Na ja. </event>
      <event start="T328-549" end="T329-03">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T341-421" end="T341-938">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T342-586" end="T342-876">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T344-837" end="T107">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T107" end="T346-788">oki [nerazumljivo]. </event>
      <event start="T359-344" end="T359-974">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T360-567" end="T361-072">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T373-607" end="T375-732">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T377-471" end="T378-021">Ja. </event>
