      <event start="T1027-038" end="T1027-652">Okej. </event>
      <event start="T1028-534" end="T1029-369">Ne. </event>
      <event start="T1031-338" end="T1031-842">Okej. </event>
      <event start="T1035-778" end="T1036-365">Ja? </event>
      <event start="T1040-992" end="T1042-2">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1044-004" end="T1044-473">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1061-327" end="T1061-882">Zakaj? </event>
      <event start="T1067-923" end="T1068-367">Okej. </event>
      <event start="T1069-21" end="T340">To je kar ... </event>
      <event start="T340" end="T1070-615">nnn ... [zvok] </event>
      <event start="T1070-615" end="T1072-315">not gonna say. </event>
      <event start="T1072-315" end="T1073-268">Nič ne+bom rekla. </event>
      <event start="T1073-268" end="T1074-523">Nič ne+bom rekla. </event>
      <event start="T1074-523" end="T1076-424">K bo malo eee kontroverzno. </event>
      <event start="T1080-301" end="T1081-608">Ja ja. </event>
      <event start="T1083-5" end="T343">Še dobro, </event>
      <event start="T343" end="T1085-697">jaz tudi še dobro, da nisem. </event>
      <event start="T1085-697" end="T1086-858">Še dobro, da nisem. </event>
      <event start="T1089-617" end="T1090-481">Hot vampir. </event>
      <event start="T1091-715" end="T1092-922">Saj. </event>
      <event start="T1092-922" end="T1094-114">Pa še to, </event>
      <event start="T1094-114" end="T346">kva je, </event>
      <event start="T346" end="T1095-438">kako je že njej ime? </event>
      <event start="T1096-274" end="T347">Bella, </event>
      <event start="T347" end="T1098-214">pač, jaz bi hotela biti ona. </event>
      <event start="T1099-852" end="T1101-610">Pa tako tam živeti v temu mestecu. </event>
      <event start="T1101-610" end="T1102-178">Odfuk. </event>
      <event start="T1111-569" end="T353">No, </event>
      <event start="T353" end="T1112-904">do tja pa nisem prišla. </event>
      <event start="T1114-371" end="T1115-889">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1118-739" end="T1119-192">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1122-862" end="T1123-466">Pa ziher ni. </event>
      <event start="T1126-614" end="T1127-688">O, ne. </event>
      <event start="T1127-688" end="T1128-311">O, ne. </event>
      <event start="T1134-524" end="T1134-786">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1141-845" end="T1143-647">Kako se že temu reče? </event>
      <event start="T1145-138" end="T1145-692">Ja ja. </event>
      <event start="T1146-369" end="T1147-643">Uncanny valley. </event>
      <event start="T1151-172" end="T366">Ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T366" end="T367">meni se zdi, da če bi gledala </event>
      <event start="T367" end="T1155-648">eem ... </event>
      <event start="T1155-648" end="T368">Kva sem zd(), </event>
      <event start="T368" end="T369">kaj sem zdaj gledala, k sem bila tudi tako, </event>
      <event start="T369" end="T1161-328">če bi jaz to gledala, k bi bila tako mlajša ... </event>
      <event start="T1161-328" end="T1163-134">Ne bi bilo dobro. </event>
      <event start="T1163-134" end="T1163-941">Tako Hunger, </event>
      <event start="T1163-941" end="T370">ja, </event>
      <event start="T370" end="T1165-271">Hunger Games. </event>
      <event start="T1165-271" end="T1167-023">Zadnjič sem gledala Hunger Games. </event>
      <event start="T1167-023" end="T1168-510">Kako se temu reče? </event>
      <event start="T1169-537" end="T1170-253">Igre lakote. </event>
      <event start="T1172-121" end="T1173-634">Še dobro, da tega nisem prej gledala. </event>
      <event start="T1175-826" end="T1176-411">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1176-411" end="T371">Sam je bila tako ... </event>
      <event start="T371" end="T1178-978">this is so deep. [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T1179-655" end="T1179-938">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1181-396" end="T373">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T373" end="T1183-126">To bi bila jaz pač. </event>
      <event start="T1183-937" end="T1186-593">Po moje, da bi bila že bolj radicalised kakor zdaj. </event>
      <event start="T1186-593" end="T1189-393">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1189-393" end="T1190-604">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1197-425" end="T1200-637">Jaz, če ne bi imela mojih emo ... skupin. </event>
      <event start="T1211-11" end="T382">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T382" end="T1212-826">is it's not just how you look. [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T1216-266" end="T1218-778">[smeh] To, kar je v tebi, je pomembno. </event>
      <event start="T1227-262" end="T1228-13">To pa ne vem. </event>
      <event start="T1229-435" end="T1229-925">True. </event>
      <event start="T1231-536" end="T1232-189">To je resnica. </event>
      <event start="T1233-34" end="T1236-926">[smeh] </event>
    </tier>
